### ============================================================
### PAYMENTS — Create Payment, Pay with Wallet, Get Payment
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### All user-facing endpoints require a valid JWT access token
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@otherUserToken = PASTE_OTHER_USER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# CREATE PAYMENT (card/apple pay/mada — initiates Paylink)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Create Payment — credit card for invoice (returns Paylink URL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice_id": 1,
  "user_id": 1,
  "amount": 15000,
  "payment_method": "credit_card"
}

###

### [SUCCESS] Create Payment — mada card for invoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice_id": 1,
  "user_id": 1,
  "amount": 15000,
  "payment_method": "mada"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Create Payment — user_id mismatch (400 User ID must match)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice_id": 1,
  "user_id": 9999,
  "amount": 15000,
  "payment_method": "credit_card"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Create Payment — access another user's invoice (403 Access denied)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice_id": 1,
  "user_id": 2,
  "amount": 15000,
  "payment_method": "credit_card"
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Create Payment — wallet method via wrong endpoint (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice_id": 1,
  "user_id": 1,
  "amount": 15000,
  "payment_method": "wallet"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Create Payment — no token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoice_id": 1,
  "user_id": 1,
  "amount": 15000,
  "payment_method": "credit_card"
}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# PAY WITH WALLET (wallet balance deduction)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Pay with Wallet — no promo code
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/pay-with-wallet/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [SUCCESS] Pay with Wallet — with valid promo code
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/pay-with-wallet/1?coupon_code=SAVE10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Pay with Wallet — another user's invoice (403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/pay-with-wallet/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Pay with Wallet — invalid coupon code (400 Invalid coupon)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/pay-with-wallet/1?coupon_code=FAKECODE999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Pay with Wallet — no token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/pay-with-wallet/1


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET PAYMENT BY ID (requires JWT — owner only)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Payment — owner accesses own payment
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Payment — IDOR: another user tries to access (403 Access denied)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Get Payment — non-existent payment ID (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET MY PAYMENTS (requires JWT)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get My Payments — paginated payment history
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/my-payments?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get My Payments — no token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/my-payments


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET PAYMENTS BY INVOICE (requires JWT — invoice owner only)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Payments by Invoice — own invoice
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/invoice/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Payments by Invoice — IDOR with another user (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/invoice/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# PAYLINK CALLBACK (webhook — no auth required, called by Paylink)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Paylink Callback — simulate paid status
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/paylink-callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionNo": "TXN-123456",
  "orderStatus": "paid"
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Paylink Callback — missing transactionNo (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/paylink-callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderStatus": "paid"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Paylink Callback — fake transaction trying to mark paid (404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/paylink-callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionNo": "FAKE-TXN-999999",
  "orderStatus": "paid"
}
